{
  "stem": "4963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I know now that, you know, it's not-- you know, that's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nevertheless, I mean, that feeling haunted me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at the same time, I said it's, you know, that it's an adventure, and life is really an adventure.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and it's-- whatever happens will be OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I really believe that there was a, a fate and that we cannot fight it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I should go along but at the same time look out for myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I went on into different periods of my life, I, I blocked out things, and I put things behind because I said, I have to move on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as things came up, I didn't really fight them, but I said-- but I didn't fight to change it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at the same time, I fought the survival instinct.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And within about two months, we were-- even in months, we were placed in the ghetto, which was, I would say, about 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was across a bridge, I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we all were with wagons and-- I don't think-- maybe cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went into this place, into this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a barbed wire that was built around it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I do remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember there was a [NON-ENGLISH] ghetto and a, and a [NON-ENGLISH] ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were at first in the [NON-ENGLISH] ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, [NON-ENGLISH] ghetto is-- means small and [NON-ENGLISH] means big.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we-- I went to live with my Aunt [NON-ENGLISH] with her, her three children, Wolf, Genia, and Liena, and also with my Uncle Osher, Aunt Chassia, and [NON-ENGLISH], their little boy.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a small house, as I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we lived on the second story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was, consisted, I think, of one room with a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
